title: Keity Shares Her Solo Date Experience After Being Stood Up
description:
Our producer Keity was excited to go out with an old friend. But once the day arrived, the woman went ghost! She ignored her texts and calls. What did Keity do? She went through with her plans and turned it into a great experience. Listen!
